<paragraph blockId="0.[1256,2135,688,1311]" pageId="0" pageNumber="448">• Large mammals with big head and thick neck, small eyes, rounded ears, no facial vibrissae; muscular bodies with stout legs, large paws, and short tail.</paragraph>
